# videoTracks

**Instance Property**

The tracks from which the output reads the composited video.

## Declaration

```swift
var videoTracks: [AVAssetTrack] { get }
```

## Discussion

The array contains [doc://com.apple.avfoundation/documentation/AVFoundation/AVAssetTrack] objects owned by the target asset reader’s asset.

## Inspecting an output

- **videoSettings**: The video settings that the output uses.
